trans-unit.source: Represents a single [Target](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) element in an [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/add/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] project.
trans-unit.target: Representerar en enskild [mål](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) element i ett [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/add/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] projekt.

trans-unit.source: Adds the specified [Task](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) element to the [Target](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) element.
trans-unit.target: Lägger till den angivna [aktivitet](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) elementet så att den [mål](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) element.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildTask"></xref> object that represents the <xref uid="langword_csharp_Task" name="Task" href=""></xref> element to add to the <xref uid="langword_csharp_Target" name="Target" href=""></xref> element.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildTask"> </xref> objekt som representerar den <xref uid="langword_csharp_Task" name="Task" href=""> </xref> elementet ska läggas till i <xref uid="langword_csharp_Target" name="Target" href=""> </xref> element.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildTask"></xref> object represents a child `Task` element of the `Target` element.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildTask"> </xref> -objektet representerar en underordnad `Task` element i den `Target` element.

trans-unit.source: Gets the `Condition` attribute value of the [Target](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) element.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar den `Condition` attributvärdet för den [mål](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) element.

trans-unit.source: The `Condition` attribute value of the `Target` element.
trans-unit.target: Den `Condition` attributvärdet för den `Target` element.

trans-unit.source: Gets the `DependsOnTargets` attribute value of the [Target](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) element, which is a semicolon-separated list.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar den `DependsOnTargets` attributvärdet för den [mål](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) element som är en semikolonavgränsad lista.

trans-unit.source: The `DependsOnTargets` attribute value of the `Target` element.
trans-unit.target: Den `DependsOnTargets` attributvärdet för den `Target` element.

trans-unit.source: Gets an enumerator that iterates through the <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildTask"></xref> objects in the <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar en uppräknare går igenom den <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildTask"> </xref> objekt i den <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: This method allows the caller to use the `foreach` statement of the C# language (`for each` in [!INCLUDE[vbprvb](~/add/includes/vbprvb-md.md)]) to iterate through the individual <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildTask> objects in the <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target>.
trans-unit.target: Den här metoden kan anroparen att använda den `foreach` satsen i C#-språk (`for each` i [!INCLUDE[vbprvb](~/add/includes/vbprvb-md.md)]) att gå igenom de enskilda <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildTask>objekt i <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target>.</xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target> </xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildTask>

trans-unit.source: A <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildTask> object represents a child element of the `Target` element.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildTask>-objektet representerar ett underordnat element för den `Target` element.</xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildTask>

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator> for the <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildTask"></xref> objects in the <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator>för den <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildTask"> </xref> objekt i den <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target"> </xref>.</xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the items that are to be input into this target.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger de objekt som ska vara indata för det här målet.

trans-unit.source: Items inside this target attribute are used as the inputs in the top level dependency analysis.
trans-unit.target: Objekt i den här målattribut används som indata i den översta nivån beroende analysen.

trans-unit.source: A string representing the items.
trans-unit.target: En sträng som representerar objekten.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating whether the [Target](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) element was imported into the project.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar ett värde som anger om den [mål](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) element har importerats till projektet.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the `Target` element was imported into the project; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Om den `Target` element har importerats till projektet, annars <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets the `Name` attribute value of the [Target](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) element.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar den `Name` attributvärdet för den [mål](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) element.

trans-unit.source: The `Name` attribute value of the `Target` element.
trans-unit.target: Den `Name` attributvärdet för den `Target` element.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the expected outputs of this target.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger de förväntade utdata för det här målet.

trans-unit.source: You can apply transforms to this target attribute to transform a set of input items into a set of output items.
trans-unit.target: Du kan använda transformeringar till detta målattribut för att omvandla en uppsättning inkommande objekt till en uppsättning objekt som utdata.

trans-unit.source: This attribute is used not only for top level dependency analysis but also for the purposes of defining this targets outputs.
trans-unit.target: Det här attributet används inte bara för övre nivå beroende analys, utan också i syfte att definiera mål-utdata.

trans-unit.source: A string representing the outputs.
trans-unit.target: En sträng som representerar utdata.

trans-unit.source: Removes the specified [Task](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) element from the [Target](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) element.
trans-unit.target: Tar bort den angivna [aktivitet](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) element från den [mål](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) element.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildTask> object represents a child `Task` element of the `Target` element.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildTask>-objektet representerar en underordnad `Task` element i den `Target` element.</xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildTask>

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildTask"></xref> object that represents the <xref uid="langword_csharp_Task" name="Task" href=""></xref> element to remove from the <xref uid="langword_csharp_Target" name="Target" href=""></xref> element.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.BuildTask"> </xref> objekt som representerar den <xref uid="langword_csharp_Task" name="Task" href=""> </xref> element ska tas bort från den <xref uid="langword_csharp_Target" name="Target" href=""> </xref> element.
